# Algorithm-trainer

Title: Algorithms Trainer (CLI)
What: Generate interview-style tasks, submit answers, track progress
Features: Topics, random tasks, answer checker, stats, export
Install: pip install -e .
Run: algotrainer topics, algotrainer new dijkstra
Dev: pytest, ruff
Roadmap: list topics + upcoming
